data.description: Don't miss out on the chance to own this cozy townhome in Margate. The home features a 3-bedroom, 2 and a half-bathroom layout along with a convenient parking. The unit is equipped with it's own washer and dryer. Seller is in the process of adding a new roof. Enjoy the privacy of fenced-in backyard and the convenience of being the corner lot. Nestled on a tranquil street, this property boasts an ideal location for quiet and friendly neighborhood.
